{"tid":1314310,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] 英國曼城(曼徹斯特)連儂牆!! 請廣傳!!","createTime":"2019-07-14T06:17:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T23:35:36.000Z","uid":128590,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d722d3b57045db0a208883c82b6ee111efdeb954","tid":1314310,"uid":128590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T06:17:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fqXZYxp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfqXZYxp.jpg&h=448f21cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iQGW0LL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiQGW0LL.jpg&h=98301914&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n地點: 曼徹斯特唐人街 牌坊對面 China Buffet Restaurant對開<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">好緊要!! 好緊要!! 大家經過請影張相!! 因為要知道多唔多人寫memo或者幾時比人拆左!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n如果儘可能就預備print出黎既野加上去/修補/替換 因為最快比人拆既通常都係標題果張<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n歡迎取用下一個comment既標題圖 就咁print出黎就得...<br />\n<br />\n請英國巴絲多多支持!! 一定要廣傳!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要貼到周圍都有!! 製造輿論 遍地開花!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n伯明翰連儂牆<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1313573\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1313573</a><br />\n<br />\n第二次倫敦連儂牆<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1311426\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1311426</a><br />\n<br />\n第一次倫敦連儂牆 (已被拆)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1309632\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1309632</a>"},{"pid":"0f96ff6e571f6b4864a2459bb5f9211465ec821b","tid":1314310,"uid":128590,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T06:18:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ec2ZYAA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2